Class AnonynousEclipseLinkStateObjectVisitor

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.persistence.jpa.jpql.tools.model.query.AnonymousStateObjectVisitor

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class AnonynousEclipseLinkStateObjectVisitor extends AnonymousStateObjectVisitor implements EclipseLinkStateObjectVisitor
This visitor allows a subclass to simply override AnonymousStateObjectVisitor.visit(StateObject) and perform the same task for all visited ItateObjects.
